description: This class div contains the whole interview
This class div contains the 'startInterview' class button (Start Interview) that opens the interview page
This class div contains the interview in the interview page and it's in charge of dividing the screen - one side is the side of the interview itself
column3: and the other side is the tags

description: This class div contains the interview itself (the left side of the screen)
This class div contains the 'divBtnShowTags' class div and 'tagsDiv' class div(the right side of the screen)
This class div contains the 'btnShowTags' class button (Show Current Tags (intermediate result)) that shows the tags
This class div contains the tags
This class div contains the 'restartBtn' class button (Home) that returns to the home page and restarts the interview and data
This class div contains the 'btnStart' class button (Start) that starts the interview and the 'btn' buttons that each represent an answer
This class div contains the 'feedbackBtn' class button (Write Feedback) that opens the feedback input
This class div contains the 'inputNameID' id input and the 'inputID' id input
This class div contains the 'btnShowTranscript' class button (Show Transcript) that shows the transcript of the interview when clicked
This class div contains the transcript and the 'btnRevisitQ' class button (Revisit this question)
This class div contains the 'btnConclusion' class button (Show Conclusion) that opens the conclusion page
This class div contains the 'btnDownloadTranscript' class button (Download Transcript) that download the transcript
This class div contains the conclusions
This class div contains the 'btnDownloadConclusions' class button (Download Conclusions) that download the conclusions
This class div contains the 'backToWelcomePage' class button (Home) that returns to the home page and restarts the interview and data
